{"tid":2426561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【民陣吹大雞】明日早上9點半西九龍裁判法院見！","createTime":"2021-02-28T07:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T07:50:19.000Z","uid":289257,"like":46,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9849ec3539981e7a8c290aff57cb0eae3d0a4b75","tid":2426561,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"#緊急呼籲<br />\n<br />\n各位香港市民，參與初選的朋友今天被正式起訴顛覆國家政權罪。過去我們曾經有二百萬人走上街頭，有超過六十萬人參與初選投票，今天被控的不只有他們，而是所有爭取民主、自由的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n我們呼籲各位香港人，明天早上9時半抽空一起到西九龍裁判法院，先以排隊入法院的方式，企滿西九龍裁判法院，聲援被捕被控的手足！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線召集人<br />\n陳皓桓<br />\n<br />\nSource: #民陣 FB<br />\n#五大訴求 #缺一不可<br />\n#釋放所有政治犯<br />\n#政治打壓可恥<br />\n#初選大搜捕 #濫捕 #初選 #候選人 #國安法 #法治已死 #兩制已亡 #自治全失 #香港人平安"},{"pid":"0e946ffd885ee6d582e5b9e99240263dc6120bb1","tid":2426561,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993276d7f775611590d91b4451f737f74ba9c948","tid":2426561,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f27473178553f8cf12ed5df9d62febf56c8f31","tid":2426561,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8857fcceb617d0276636a8c4df6952211bb40a6f","tid":2426561,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05be3874ed052a55a87fddf8734f65d5915c460","tid":2426561,"uid":309558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:21:46.000Z","msg":